1. *Srcem* sam uz tebe. (I am with you with all my heart.)
2. Njegova odluka *srcem* nije bila prihvaćena. (His decision wasn't accepted with the heart.)
3. *Srcem* verujem u ljubav. (I believe in love with all my heart.)
4. Iako je bila umorna, radila je *srcem*. (Although she was tired, she worked with her heart.)
5. Srećan sam *srcem* što si se vratila. (I'm happy with all my heart that you're back.)
6. Učini to *srcem*, ne samo iz obaveze. (Do it with your heart, not just out of obligation.)
7. Njeni roditelji *srcem* su je podržavali u svemu. (Her parents supported her in everything with all their hearts.)
8. *Srcem* se nadam da ćeš uspeti. (I hope with all my heart that you'll succeed.)
9. Njegov *srcem* izbor bio je pogrešan. (His choice was wrong with all his heart.)
10. Pevač je izveo pesmu *srcem* i oduševio publiku. (The singer performed the song with all his heart and impressed the audience.)